thread.title_full: Freeze Pro Shop reviewed by Cape Cod Skiier

author: Cape Cod Skiier
title: Cape Cod Skiier
text: Good experience everything came on time and as ordered. Some of the best pricing when checking competitors sites. Had to pay for shipping..was almost the reason why I didn't go with Free Pro, would like to have seen some incentive to make it more attractive for us Yanks. This was the only reason for 4 not 5 stars.
